  &lt;p&gt;Vue is a good tool that gives us an opportunity to learn more about the framework. The &lt;strong&gt;framework&lt;/strong&gt; is well used and skillful. When we are no longer satisfied with the surface, we can learn more about it.For example, how does vue implement &lt;strong&gt;data binding&lt;/strong&gt;, how does it implement deeper technical principles such as &lt;strong&gt;data response&lt;/strong&gt;.That makes a lot of sense&lt;/p&gt;
